    An interior Node of the spatial index that contains up to four quadrant objects, each of which could be another Node, a Leaf or null (if the quadrant is outside the polygon).
    PolygonSpatialIndex
    A PolygonSpatialIndex indexes a polygon with a quad-tree-like structure that allows for fast containment testing with PolygonSpatialIndex.containment(Location).
